spec.md:259:- **Determinism.** Tests must be reproducible. Network-dependent tests are not allowed except where they declare an `allowed-docker-image` and run against that pre-pulled image with networking disabled.\ndocs/tck.md:103:| `checkAllowedDockerImages` | Scan allowed images for vulnerabilities with grype, either all images or only those changed between two commits (§CI-scan-docker-images). |\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/gradle.properties:4:library.coordinates = org.neo4j.driver:neo4j-java-driver:5.28.5\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/gradle.properties:6:metadata.dir = org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/build.gradle:14:    testImplementation \"org.neo4j.driver:neo4j-java-driver:$libraryVersion\"\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/user-code-filter.json:7:      \"includeClasses\" : \"org.neo4j.driver.**\"\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/user-code-filter.json:10:      \"includeClasses\" : \"org_neo4j_driver.neo4j_java_driver.**\"\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/settings.gradle:20:rootProject.name = 'org.neo4j.driver.neo4j-java-driver_tests'\ndocs/ci.md:89:### CI-scan-docker-images: Scan Docker images\ndocs/ci.md:91:On PRs touching `allowed-docker-images/**`, runs `checkAllowedDockerImages`\ndocs/ci.md:96:### CI-sync-docker-images: Sync Docker images\ndocs/ci.md:98:On PRs touching `allowed-docker-images/**` (Dependabot updates), synchronizes\ndocs/ci.md:209:- **Docker isolation** — `disable-docker.sh` / `restore-docker.sh`, plus\ndocs/ci.md:210:  `dockerd.service` and `discard-port.conf`. After allowed images are pulled, CI\ndocs/DEVELOPING.md:16:- Docker (required for pulling/using allowed images during tests). Needs to work without `sudo`: `sudo usermod -aG docker $USER` and reboot.\ndocs/DEVELOPING.md:17:- [`grype`](https://github.com/anchore/grype) version `0.104.0` for scanning docker images:\nd